title: How can I fix a transfer between my previous Pixel 2 to a new Pixel 2?
content:
The cord connection never worked between my 2 devices so I used the option to transfer via Google account and confirmed the shapes on both devices.

Unfortunately, I only got text messages from 2 months ago and back to 2017, not the text messages from 2 months ago to today. 

How can I fix this? (it even seems the arrangement of my apps are outdated to what it looked like a few months ago)

Thank you
